                    "$$ \\mathbf{F}_{12} + \\mathbf{F}_{21} = \\mathbf{0}, $$",
                    "e quindi, dalle relazioni (4.31), segue:",
                    "$$ \\frac{d\\mathbf{p}_1}{dt} + \\frac{d\\mathbf{p}_2}{dt} = \\frac{d}{dt}(\\mathbf{p}_1 + \\mathbf{p}_2) = \\frac{d\\mathbf{p}_t}{dt} = \\mathbf{0}, $$",
                    "dove",
                    "$$ \\mathbf{p}_t \\equiv \\mathbf{p}_1 + \\mathbf{p}_2 $$",
