                    "$$ \\mathbf{L} = \\mathbf{L}' + \\mathbf{r}_{CM} \\times (m\\mathbf{v}_{CM}), $$",
                    "$$ E_k = E_k' + \\frac{1}{2} m v_{CM}^2. $$",
