                    "$$ e^2 \\left( \\frac{1}{2} m_1 v_{1i}'^2 + \\frac{1}{2} m_2 v_{2i}'^2 \\right) = \\frac{1}{2} m_1 v_{1f}'^2 + \\frac{1}{2} m_2 v_{2f}'^2, \\hspace{4cm} \\tag{8.9} $$",
                    "da cui segue (Nota 4):",
                    "$$ v_{1f}' = -e v_{1i}', \\hspace{4cm} \\tag{8.10} $$",
