                    "$$ W = Q_1 + Q_2. $$",
                    "Pertanto, siccome $V_B/V_A = V_C/V_D$, l’efficienza del processo vale:",
                    "$$ \\xi = \\frac{Q_1}{|W|} = \\frac{Q_1}{|Q_1 + Q_2|} = \\frac{nRT_1 \\ln \\frac{V_C}{V_D}}{nRT_2 \\ln \\frac{V_B}{V_A} - nRT_1 \\ln \\frac{V_C}{V_D}} = \\frac{T_1}{T_2 - T_1}, $$",
